item.title: QF4-14-010220
item.description:
Alert Level: Advice.
Location: Dundowran Rd & Newbauers Rd, Walligan.
Reported: 28/01/2014 1:27:21 PM.
Current Status: Going.
Details:

Update sent at 4pm

Walligan (Hervey Bay) – vegetation fire

Multiple Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) crews are responding to a vegetation fire on Hornes Road at Walligan. The fire has been burning within containment lines for several days but broke containment lines around 3pm. There is no threat to property from this fire but the blaze is causing a lot of smoke in the area. Motorists are advised to be cautious and drive to the conditions. Residents should close windows and doors and if suffering from a respiratory condition, keep medication close by.
item.author: Queensland Fire & Rescue Service
